# RTMA | Real-time Music Analysis

## Install

`pip install rtma`

## How to use

```
fn = "data/guitar_electronic_010-065-127.wav"
n_fft = 2048
hop_length = 512
win_length = 256

x, sr = load_audio(fn)
play_audio(x, sr)
```

```
plot_audio(x, sr)
```

```
mx, px = calc_spectrums(x, n_fft, hop_length, win_length)
```
